    "Page Two THE AUGUSTA COURIER He who spares no ciass of men is angry at no person but the rices of all 1300 Southern Finance Building Augusta Georgia SecondClass Postage Paid at Augusta Georgia SUBSCRIPTION RATE Published Weekly by The Courier Publishing Company Year 400 HOW MANY MUST BE MUGGED The Tampa Florida Tribune January 28 1963 Many Congressmen regard the House District of Columbia Committee as a sort of booby prize to which freshmen and outoffavor members are assigned because every Representative is entitled to be on at least one committee Rep Harlan Hagen California Democrat now serving his sixth term possibly has regarded the committee in that light in the past but right now its a good bet hed prefer at least for a time a seat on it to his position on the House Agriculture Committee For Congressman Hagen has acquired a personal interest in better government for the district or at least better police protection He was mugged early Friday morning while leaving a night club in the northcast section knocked down by several assailants and robbed of a wallet which he estimated contained 3O The assault on the Congressman is scarcely unique Earlier in the"
